      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Steven Atkinson</b>\n</p><p><b>Steven Atkinson</b>,<br />\nan Australian university graduate in mathematics and computer science and hobby programmer from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Brisbane\">Brisbane</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>. \nHe is author of the chess <a href=\"/GUI\" title=\"GUI\">GUI</a> <a href=\"/Scid_vs._PC\" title=\"Scid vs. PC\">Scid vs. PC</a>, written in <a href=\"/index.php?title=Tcl-Tk&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Tcl-Tk (page does not exist)\">Tcl/Tk</a>, which acts as <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Front_and_back_ends\">front end</a> of a <a href=\"/Databases\" title=\"Databases\">database</a> back end, a fork of <a href=\"/Shane_Hudson\" title=\"Shane Hudson\">Shane Hudson's</a> Chess Information Database (<a href=\"/SCID\" title=\"SCID\">SCID</a>).\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2015_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2015 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Steven_Atkinson&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Steven_Atkinson&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=36388\">Scid fork and Phalanx news</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Steven Atkinson</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 17, 2010&#160;» <a href=\"/Phalanx\" title=\"Phalanx\">Phalanx</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=41136\">Scid vs. PC 4.6</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Steven Atkinson</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 19, 2011</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=44754\">Scid vs. PC 4.8</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Steven Atkinson</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 10, 2012</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=50272\">Scid vs. PC 4.11</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Steven Atkinson</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 29, 2013</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=52127\">New Phalanx code</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Steven Atkinson</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 26, 2014&#160;» <a href=\"/Phalanx\" title=\"Phalanx\">Phalanx</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2015_...\">2015 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Steven_Atkinson&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2015 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=55910\">Scid vs. PC 4.14</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Steven Atkinson</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 05, 2015</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=59027\">Scid vs. PC 4.16</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Steven Atkinson</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 24, 2016</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=65815\">Scid vs PC with CQL, build issue</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Steven Atkinson</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 25, 2017&#160;» <a href=\"/Chess_Query_Language\" title=\"Chess Query Language\">CQL</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=66562\">Scid vs PC CQL 5.2 feature</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Steven Atkinson</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 11, 2018</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=71135\">Scid vs. PC - EPD Export feature</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Steven Atkinson</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 29, 2019&#160;» <a href=\"/Extended_Position_Description\" title=\"Extended Position Description\">Extended Position Description</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Steven_Atkinson&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://sourceforge.net/blog/after-scid-row-a-new-chess-app-is-born/\">After Scid row, a new chess app is born | SourceForge Community Blog</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://steven-atkinson.software.informer.com/\">Steven Atkinson Software Informer: Latest Steven Atkinson software updates and reviews: Scid vs PC, etc.</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Steven_Atkinson&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://scidvspc.sourceforge.net/#toc8\">Scid vs. PC - Contact</a> </span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one Level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301095836\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.006 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.006 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 37/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 74/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw1-mw_:pcache:idhash:5967-0!canoni